'''约翰·格斯查'''（{{lang|en|'''John Goscha'''}}，{{bd|1984年|3月19日||}}），是一名美国发明家和企业家，他是美国终极灯泡公司（{{lang|en|Finally Light Bulb Company }}）的首席执行官，该公司发明了革新的灯泡产品Acandescence。他还是{{le|IdeaPaint|IdeaPaint}}的创始人。

==生平==
[[File:Acandescent_Light_Bulb.tif|thumbnail]]

他毕业于{{le|里吉斯耶稣会高中|Regis Jesuit High School}}，并在2006年毕业于[[巴布森学院|巴布森学院]]经济和企业专业，毕业后他组建IdeaPaint<ref>{{cite web  | last=American Made Heroes  | title=Welcome to IdeaPaint of Ashland, Massachusetts  | url=http://www.americanmadeheroes.com/AMH-state-massachusetts.html  | accessdate=19 June 2012  | archive-date=2016-03-04  | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075029/http://www.americanmadeheroes.com/AMH-state-massachusetts.html  | dead-url=no  }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| last=Bloomberg| title=Ready To Erase Whiteboards, IdeaPain Lands 1,700 Lowe’s Stores| url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-25/ready-to-erase-whiteboards-ideapaint-lands-1-700-lowe-s-stores.html| accessdate=11 June 2012| archive-date=2015-01-05| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150105113540/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-25/ready-to-erase-whiteboards-ideapaint-lands-1-700-lowe-s-stores.html| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last=Bezinga | title=Hitting The Big Time: IdeaPaint Arrives in 1,700 Lowe’s Locations | url=http://www.benzinga.com/generallifemisc/movers-shakers/11/05/1112831/hitting-the-big-time-ideapaint-arrives-in-1-700-lowes-l | accessdate=19 June 2012 | archive-date=2016-03-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305173502/http://www.benzinga.com/generallifemisc/movers-shakers/11/05/1112831/hitting-the-big-time-ideapaint-arrives-in-1-700-lowes-l | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last=Fast Company | title=IdeaPaint: Turn Your Entire Office Into A Whiteboard | url=http://www.fastcompany.com/blog/cliff-kuang/design-innovation/ideapaint-turn-your-entire-office-whiteboard | accessdate=19 June 2012 | archive-date=2012-07-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120726070108/http://www.fastcompany.com/blog/cliff-kuang/design-innovation/ideapaint-turn-your-entire-office-whiteboard | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

格斯查之后创建并担任终极灯泡公司总裁，并开发新能源以减损能耗<ref>{{cite web | last=Sorkanich | title=This Super-Efficient Lightbulb Uses Tesla Tech for an Incandescent Glow | url=http://gizmodo.com/this-super-efficient-lightbulb-uses-tesla-tech-for-an-i-1609644357 | access-date=2015-01-05 | archive-date=2021-01-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130050401/https://gizmodo.com/this-super-efficient-lightbulb-uses-tesla-tech-for-an-i-1609644357 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。该公司推出的Acandescent[[无极灯|无极灯泡]]效果类似[[白炽灯|白炽灯]]，但效率要高出75%，并比其寿命长15倍<ref>{{cite web | last=Stevenson | title=The Next Great Light Bulb | url=http://www.slate.com/articles/technology/technology/2014/08/best_led_light_bulbs_finally_bulb_how_to_replace_the_incandescent_with_something.2.html | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821035840/http://www.slate.com/articles/technology/technology/2014/08/best_led_light_bulbs_finally_bulb_how_to_replace_the_incandescent_with_something.2.html | archivedate=2014年8月21日 | df= }}</ref>。

2009年，格斯查被提名《{{le|公司杂志|Inc. (magazine)}}》“30 Under 30”（“30大30岁以下企业家”）<ref>{{cite web| last=Inc.| title=30 Under 30| url=http://www.inc.com/30under30/2009/profile_ideapaint.html| accessdate=11 June 2012| archive-date=2020-10-22| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022214520/https://www.inc.com/30under30/2009/profile_ideapaint.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>，名列《[[商业周刊|商业周刊]]》的“美国最佳年轻企业家”之一<ref>{{cite web | last=Umass Lowell | title=MassChallenge Lowell Unpanel Entrepreneur Event | url=http://www.uml.edu/student-services/career_services/Hot_News/UnPanel_MassChallenge_Event.html | accessdate=19 June 2012 | archive-date=2011-04-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110408152353/http://www.uml.edu/student-services/career_services/Hot_News/UnPanel_MassChallenge_Event.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| last=Forbes| title=30 Under 30| url=http://www.forbes.com/pictures/lmf45kde/john-goscha-founder-ideapaint-27/| accessdate=11 June 2012| archive-date=2015-01-05| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150105113508/http://www.forbes.com/pictures/lmf45kde/john-goscha-founder-ideapaint-27/| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

他的产品IdeaPaint也被视为2008年芝加哥新保守主义贸易展览会的最佳发明<ref>{{cite web| last=2 Modern| title=Best of NeoCon Innovations Award: IdeaPaint| url=http://blog.2modern.com/2008/10/best-of-neocon.html| accessdate=11 June 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202103049/http://blog.2modern.com/2008/10/best-of-neocon.html| archive-date=2014-02-02| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2011年，它也荣获新英格兰发明奖<ref>{{cite web | last=SBANE – Small Business Association of New England | title=SBANE Breakfast Series Kicks Off New Season with Painting Magic Into Profit | url=http://www.sbane.org/index.php?s=ideapaint | accessdate=6 June 2012 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201165252/http://www.sbane.org/index.php?s=ideapaint | archivedate=2014年2月1日 }}</ref>。

